Requires node version >= 20
Added support for Floodlight Cam E340 (T8425; #428)
Added support for Solar Wall Light Cam S120 (T84A0; #406)
Added support for Indoor Cam S350 (T8416; #403)
Added support for eufyCam E330 (Professional; T8600; #391)

Fixed issues #371, #376, #379, #380, #387, #420, #422, #432
